        "title": "ON THE VINES",
        "video-sec-content-txt-1": "<p>Sourced from a 20-year-old vineyard rooted in ancient limestone soils, Alvi’s Drift Verreaux Black Eagle Pinotage 2023 reflects the power of terroir. These mineral-rich soils provide the ideal foundation for grapes to produce a wine of exceptional depth and character. The limestone influence enhances freshness, resulting in a one-of-a-kind wine that is both bold and refined – a true expression of place.</p>",
